name: Frog In A Well (chelseajoe)
description:
A short game about a frog in a well!

Made for LOWREZJAM 2022.

Tip! Keep Going Right -- Press left and right arrow keys liberally when in start screens. (Check out screenshot 4)!

Controls:

- SPACE to Jump, Select, or Interact

- Arrow Keys to navigate (and move)

Developed by Chelsea Joe.

Music created in Beepbox and sourced from Mixkit.
